Output demo/tmux-all-the-time.gif

Set Shell "bash"
Set FontSize 22
Set Width 1480
Set Height 920
Set Padding 20
Set BorderRadius 10
Set WindowBar Colorful
Set WindowBarSize 34
Set Theme "TokyoNight"
Set TypingSpeed 70ms

Hide
