Enter
Type "./demo/run-demo.sh"
Enter
Sleep 1500ms
Show

Sleep 1200ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Type "web"
Sleep 900ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Down
Sleep 900ms
Backspace 3
Sleep 400ms
Type "metrics"
Sleep 1200ms
Backspace 7
Sleep 400ms
Type "road"
Sleep 300ms
